{#-
  Passthrough chat template for base models (no role framing, no system
  prompts). Emits the concatenated content of all messages verbatim, so
  the /v1/chat/completions endpoint behaves like /v1/completions.
  Required when the policy model (SmolLM2, Llama-3.x base, etc.) ships
  with no chat_template in its tokenizer config.
-#}
{%- for message in messages -%}
{{- message['content'] -}}
{%- endfor -%}
